This nugget uses inotify to monitor any number of file system paths 
and send any changed or created files to the dispatcher for collection.

Required:
   libinotifytools0-dev (ubuntu package)

Build:
   # Update RZB_API_PATH to point to the directory you built the api.
   make
 
Usage:
   # Copy rzb.conf and update required information to point to your dispatcher
   ./fsmonitor /monitor/path /monitor/path2
